[normal]In our view, the development of the proposals for the taxation of Salaried Members of UK LLPs has been most unsatisfactory and represents a significant 
[normal]departure from HM Treasury’s approach to the making of tax policy as set out in “Tax Policy making: a new approach” (June 2010).
